OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FInjured worker recalls fear
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fas ship toppled over       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An injured worker has described the    
OL,6, "scary" moment a US naval ship tipped  
OL,7, over in a dry dock.                    
OL,9,FConstantin Pogor said he was thrown    
OL,10,Ffrom one side of the bridge of the     
OL,11,FPetrel to the other and passed out     
OL,12,Fafter cracking his ribs on a beam.     
OL,14,FHe is among 35 people who were injured 
OL,15,Fin the incident in Edinburgh in March. 
OL,17,FMr Pogor, who is being represented by  
OL,18,Flaw firm Digby Brown, suffered a       
OL,19,Fdislocated elbow and fractured pelvis  
OL,20,Fand is still undergoing treatment.     
